title: Ballade Cuntre Les Anemis De La France

description: Massive rewrite of both Steel String guitar parts. Far more open string voicing in lieu of strange non intuitive chord changes have been added. Ending riffs have been corrected and now sound as they should on the record, as well as being easier and more intuitive to play.
